<div style="position:absolute;left:25.20px;top:740.40px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">文法</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:115.80px;top:755.34px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">ほ</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:25.20px;top:759.00px" class="cls_004"><span class="cls_004">１</span><span class="cls_002">.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:64.80px;top:758.94px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">名詞</span><span class="cls_008"> </span><span class="cls_009">が</span><span class="cls_008"> </span><span class="cls_007">欲</span><span class="cls_009">しいです</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:779.34px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">這個句型是表現出說話人想要得到某物</span><span class="cls_010">（</span><span class="cls_009">或人</span><span class="cls_010">）</span><span class="cls_009">。另外也用在詢問聽話人想要什</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:799.74px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">麼時。需求的對象用助詞「が」表示「ほしい」是い形容詞。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:153.00px;top:816.54px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">とも  だち</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:208.20px;top:816.54px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">ほ</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:64.80px;top:820.14px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">①</span><span class="cls_008"> </span><span class="cls_007">わたしは</span><span class="cls_008">   </span><span class="cls_007">友達が</span><span class="cls_008">   </span><span class="cls_007">欲しいです。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:328.80px;top:822.00px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">我想交朋友。</span></div>
</div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:1%;right:1%;margin-left:1%;margin-right:1%;top:5964px;width:595px;height:842px;border-style:outset;overflow:hidden">
