<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:40.14px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">到達點。同時</span><span class="cls_010">，</span><span class="cls_009">助詞「</span><span class="cls_010">  </span><span class="cls_009">」和「でます」「おります」</span><span class="cls_010">（</span><span class="cls_009">第</span></div>
